All Implemented Interfaces:
IMetaDataEnabledFeature, IPossibleValues, ITypeDescriptor, IValidValues
public class JavaClassType
extends ObjectType
implements IPossibleValues, IValidValues

Provides possible values and validates attribute values that should be fully qualified Java types. A type can be verfified against muliple "valid-interfaces" and/or a "valid-superclass" from meta-data. Search is scoped to within the current project only. (Until https://bugs.eclipse.org/bugs/show_bug.cgi?id=142044 is fixed, only the first found will be used)
